title: Experience the music of fyield Live on KEXP today
fyield - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents fyield performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded November 30, 2023.

Songs:
Blockbuster
Holding Tight
We Hear The Call
Lungs Of Stone

Václav Havelka - Vocals, Guitar
Kryštof Kříček - Electronics, Synth
Pan Thorarensen - Electronics, Ambient

Host: Kevin Cole
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew
Audio Mixer: Kryštof Kříček
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Luke Knecht, Ettie Wahl
Editor: Jim Beckmann
